HEADWORD: Immortelle
<hw>Im`mor*telle"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Immortelles</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[F. See
<er>Immortal</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A plant with a
conspicuous, dry, unwithering involucre, as the species of
<spn>Antennaria</spn>, <spn>Helichrysum</spn>, <spn>Gomphrena</spn>,
etc. See <er>Everlasting</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
